    "26480618": {
      "title": "High-throughput assessment of microRNA activity and function using microRNA sensor and decoy libraries",
      "abstract": "Two large-scale resources for studying microRNA function are presented: one is a library of fluorescent sensors with a corresponding assay for global profiling of microRNA activity in different cell types; the other is a decoy library for suppressing microRNA activity individually or in pooled loss-of-function screens."
